title: The Fantasy Playoffs Are Here: Week 14 | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
As we head into the first round of the fantasy football playoffs, we highlight the standout performances from Week 13 (looking at you, Devante Parker), note the injuries from the weekend, and recommend our top adds (3:15). Then we discuss the players who are fool's gold in this week's Deceiving Yards and pick our streamers of the week, before wrapping up with a rousing edition of Fantasy Court (26:45).
Hosts: Danny Heifetz, Danny Kelly, and Craig Horlbeck
